    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "赵母",
        "赵范",
        "赵颜"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵范、赵母同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一家人全凭着耕种为本，\n小娇儿下田去未见回程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵颜上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放下犁拴上牛家门来进，\n见双亲泪汪汪跪在埃尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀，爷娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，为何啼哭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷娘有所不知，孩儿下田耕种，行至十字街前，有一算命先生，与儿看了一相。\n他道孩儿三日后夭寿而亡啊……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵颜哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说是三日后我儿丧命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只恐怕绝了我赵氏后根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀！那算命先生现在何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在十字街前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我二老前去哀告先生；倘有活命，也未可知。儿呀，带路！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫妈妈你那里将门带定，\n卦棚里去哀告算命的先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
