    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "你将这鹿脯酒暗暗献上",
        "我不是观世音救苦救难",
        "管辂",
        "赵母",
        "赵范",
        "赵颜",
        "这时候怎救得残生命转"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（管辂上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将身儿来至在卦棚坐定，\n算人间生和死不差毫分。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵母 （内同白） 走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵范、赵母、赵颜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小娇儿你与我把路来领，\n见先生泪汪汪跪在埃尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵范、赵母同跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，先生呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管公明坐卦棚用目观定，\n见二老泪汪汪跪在埃尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵颜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这二老是你什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二老双亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年迈之人，快快请起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二老到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小老儿名赵范六十三岁，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我二老年半百有此娇生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生道我娇儿三日丧命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望先生发慈悲搭救娇生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不是阴曹府轮回宫殿，\n我不是阴曹府掌簿判官。\n我不是西天佛法力无边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我不是观世音救苦救难、赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，先生呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我哭哭一声管先生，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叫叫一声管辂仙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娇儿我二老朝山拜顶，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娇儿我二老把香来焚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙长爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵母 （同哭头） 啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望先生发慈悲搭救娇生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见二老只哭得我心好惨，\n不由人一阵阵心内痛酸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，有了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见南北斗移奔高山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二老请起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "这时候怎救得残生命转、赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵颜有了救了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "救在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回到家去，准备鹿脯，去至终南山，有二……"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生，二什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有二位仙长在那里着棋，你将这鹿脯美酒，暗暗献上。他饮了你的酒，必要与\n你添寿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵范、赵母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问先生，那二位仙长怎样打扮？"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有一个穿白的斯文体相，\n有一个穿红的气宇轩昂。\n饮了酒必与你添寿绵长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "你将这鹿脯酒暗暗献上、赵范",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "你将这鹿脯酒暗暗献上、赵范",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞别了管先生忙往家奔，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "准备下鹿脯酒送到山林。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵范、赵母同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞别了管先生忙回家门，"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问先生唤回我所为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你把这鹿脯酒暗暗献上，\n必须要隐身形跌跪一旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙长爷你不必仔细叮咛，\n我赵颜纵一死不忘大恩。\n见仙长求增寿小心殷勤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵颜下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "管辂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这也是小赵颜不该命丧，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "管辂→赵范",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
