    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "他不该困霸王乌江命丧",
        "他不该问道路把樵哥斩丧",
        "北斗星",
        "十九岁你就该把命夭丧",
        "南斗星",
        "我这里将鹿脯暗暗献上",
        "望仙长发慈悲将寿添上",
        "淮阴侯小韩信功高智广",
        "赵颜",
        "都只为在卦棚先生看相"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（南斗星、北斗星同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观天地和日月乾坤浩荡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天连水水连天渺渺茫茫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星、北斗星",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃（南）（北）斗星君是也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "星君请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我奉了玉帝敕旨，巡查人间善恶。来此地已是南瞻部洲，今日闲暇无事，将\n历代君王之事，细表一番。"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自盘古分天地乾坤始创，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先太极分两仪八卦阴阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "按金木水火土五行方向，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先君臣后父子三纲五常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尧传舜舜传禹江山揖让，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夏桀暴商纣淫自取灭亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦始皇归一统山河执掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他不该焚诗书兴建阿房。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "楚项羽他倒有帝王之相，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他不该杀义帝强霸为王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把前朝君王事暂且慢讲，\n有一辈忠良臣细说端详：\n为什么未央宫一命身亡？"
        },
        {
          "character": "淮阴侯小韩信功高智广、北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休道那小韩信功高智广，\n他不该活埋母九里山旁。\n他不该逼高祖拜他为王。\n因此上未央宫一命身亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "他不该问道路把樵哥斩丧、他不该困霸王乌江命丧、南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "成萧何败萧何萧何该丧，\n为什么那老儿寿命延长？"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休道那汉萧何该当命丧，\n他本是忠良将寿命延长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叹不尽前朝的忠臣良将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "松林内摆棋盘散闷一场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵颜上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手捧着鹿脯酒终南山上，\n又只见二仙长分坐两厢。\n吞着气躲着身跌跪一旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我这里将鹿脯暗暗献上、南斗星、北斗星",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在石台摆棋盘一帅一将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红棋先黑棋后各占一方。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走一步当头炮千军难挡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还一个连环马士相奔忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见鹿脯酒从空而降，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想必是天赐我美味清香。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我和你棋不胜共饮佳酿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "飞来物饮几杯又有何妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我再下一盘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "战胜了好一似汉高皇上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "战败了好一似西楚霸王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "求寿哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳边厢又听得有人喧嚷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛抬头见小子跌跪道旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一小子，家住哪里，姓字名谁，到此何事？慢慢讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位仙长容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家住在城厢外绿柳村上，\n我的名叫赵颜耕种田庄。\n他道我三日后一命身亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "都只为在卦棚先生看相、南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听小子说此话倒也清亮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙家事是何人泄漏阴阳？"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，星君，你我在此着棋，凡人怎能知晓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "星君有所不知，只因凡间有一个管辂，生来一双慧眼，能知人间过去未来之事，\n定是此人引他前来，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "星君何不将他阳寿查上一查。"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我查来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "查得山西平原郡绿柳村赵范之子，名唤赵颜，前生作恶多端，今投赵门为子。\n注定大汉建安一十二年，寿活一十九岁，夭寿而亡。\n赵颜，你今年多大了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一十九岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈，完了哇，完了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫小子抬头看生死簿上，\n这上面造定了字字行行。\n这时候并无有解救良方。"
        },
        {
          "character": "十九岁你就该把命夭丧、赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "十九岁你就该把命夭丧、赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听他言吓得我魂魄飘荡，\n不由我小赵颜无有主张。\n可怜我家还有二老爷娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "望仙长发慈悲将寿添上、南斗星、北斗星",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小赵颜只哭得泪如雨降，\n可怜他家还有二老爷娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，星君！你看赵颜哭得可怜，何不将他阳寿与他添上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "星君说哪里话来。你我奉了玉帝敕旨，巡查人间善恶。私添阳寿，玉帝闻知，\n吃罪不起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上苍也有好生之德。何况你我……"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是你好吃酒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也好贪杯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彼此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一样！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "北斗星 （同笑） 啊，哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，这阳寿添得的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "添得的！"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵颜，你命活一十九岁，将这“一”字改为“九”字。寿活九十九岁，也就够\n了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，仙长，将那一岁添上，岂不是百岁老人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星、北斗星",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！贪心不足。听我等道来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本是南斗星从天而降，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本是北斗星降下天堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我掌生他掌死分亳不爽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "查人间生和死善恶昭彰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赐你子孙多富贵永享，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赐你财源盛金玉满堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赐你椿萱茂代代兴旺，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赐你一家人无有灾殃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赐你百寿图悬挂堂上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赐你九十九大寿延长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在人间休得要胡言乱讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "北斗星",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泄露了仙家事五雷身亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星、北斗星",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞别了二仙长忙下山岗，"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星、北斗星",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "星君爷唤回我所为哪桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "南斗星",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回去见了管辂，叫他从今以后，不要胡言乱语；再若胡言乱语，难免五雷击顶。\n那旁有人来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（北斗星、南斗星同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！二位仙长不见，待我望空一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵颜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手捧着百寿图忙下山岗，"
        }
